#585
Entrance to the Temple of the Greater Gods~
You are standing just within the 20 foot high doors of the Great temple. The
wealth of the gods is definetly felt here, and rumor has it that the gods 
themselves built this temple as their residence in this plane and as a final
refuge for mortals during the last battles of the cataclysm. The doors are 
held together with gold bands that are inlaid with more jewels than are in the
average kingdoms treasury. The floor is tiled alternatly with giant emerald an
ruby slices each several handspans across. In the distance, to the north you
see a large alter constructed of mithril silver and gold, overwhich appears
to hang a small patch of fog. To the south you see the city proceeding outward
until it meets the great southern forests. The whole scene instills you with
the wonder and power of what it took to make such a place.
~
