The Chamber of the High Priestess~
A high priestess of Aowan stands before you, ready to tend your wounds
for a small fee which shall be used for temple upkeep.  There is a large
golden altar surrounded by living trees on the northern end of the room,
and the ceiling is open to the sky.  As you look around the room you find
it odd to see that everything within appears to be within its natural state,
but such is the nature of the goddess of druidic knowledge.
