constantly adding new areas to explore as well as new abilities and skills.
If you have any questions, feel free to ask on chat or leave an email to
kyorlin@hotmail.com. To begin with, you have a single weapon, and for 
as long as you keep it, you should be able to gather new equipment on
your own.  If you are new to muds, type "SAY SCHOOL" to enter the tutorial
where you will learn the basics of mudding.
